          In the case of <command>MAILMIME_DISCRETE_TYPE_EXTENSION</command>,
          <command>dt_extension</command> is filled in.
          <command>MAILMIME_DISCRETE_TYPE_ERROR</command> is used internally.
        </para>

        <para>
